Lazily-evaluated stream with pipelining via the '>>' operator.

Requires Python 2.6.


INSTALL
=======

To install system-wide:

    $ sudo python ./setup.py install

or if you just need it in a project:

    $ cp ./stream.py ~/your/project


To make sure it works with your Python version, run all doctests:

    $ python ./stream.py -v


DOCUMENTATION
=============

./stream.py is well-documented with plenty of examples, both short
and long.
